Package org.hibernate.sql.ast.produce.spi

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ColumnReferenceQualifier
    Contract for things that can act as the qualifier for a SqlSelection for a given (Qualifiable)SqlSelectable.
    FromClauseAccess
    Access to TableGroup indexing.
    NonQualifiableSqlExpressable
    Specialization for SqlSelectables that do not need to be qualified by a ColumnReferenceQualifier to be treated as a SqlSelection.
    QualifiableSqlExpressable
    Specialization for SqlSelectables that need to be qualified by a ColumnReferenceQualifier to be treated as a SqlSelection.
    RootTableGroupProducer
    Contract for things that can produce the TableGroup that is the root of a from-clause
    SqlAliasBase  
    SqlAstCreationContext
    The "context" in which creation of SQL AST occurs.
    SqlAstCreationOptions  
    SqlAstCreationState  
    SqlAstDeleteDescriptor  
    SqlAstDescriptor
    Base descriptor of SQL AST, including the tree ({link Statement}) as well as other information determined while building it.
    SqlAstFunctionProducer
    Contract for functions impls that would like to control the translation of the SQM expression into the SQL AST function

    SqlAstFunctionProducer.convertToSqlAst(org.hibernate.sql.ast.produce.sqm.spi.SqmToSqlAstConverter) is the main contract here.
    SqlAstProcessingState
    Generalized access to state information relative to the "current process" of creating a SQL AST.
    SqlAstQuerySpecProcessingState  
    SqlAstSelectDescriptor
    SqlAstDescriptor specialization for select queries
    SqlAstUpdateDescriptor
    SqlAstDescriptor specialization for update queries
    SqlExpressable
    Unifying contract for things that are capable of being an expression in the SQL AST.
    SqlExpressionResolver
    Resolution of a SqlSelection reference for a given SqlSelectable.
    SqlQueryOptions  
    TableGroupJoinProducer  
    TableGroupProducer
    Marker interface for anything which produces a TableGroup
    TableReferenceContributor  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FromClauseIndex
    An index of various FROM CLAUSE resolutions.
    SqlAliasBaseManager
    Helper used in creating unique SQL table aliases for a SQL AST
    SqlSelectionExpression
    Represents a selection that is "re-used" in certain parts of the query other than the select-clause (mainly important for order-by, group-by and having).
